      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_BFE67FF0-22FB-0135-568C-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the section drop-down menu [1], select the section that should come after the section you are moving. Click the <strong>Move</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
